  103. ‌  let rec cloop arr idx f col max =
  104.     if col = Array.length idx then set arr idx (f idx)
  105.     else for j = 0 to pred max.(col) do
  106.            idx.(col) <- j;
  107.            cloop arr idx f (succ col) max
  108.          done
  109. ‌  let rec floop arr idx f col max =
  110.     if col < 0 then set arr idx (f idx)
  111.     else for j = 1 to max.(col) do
  112.            idx.(col) <- j;
  113.            floop arr idx f (pred col) max
  114.          done
  115. ‌  let init (type t) kind (layout : t layout) dims f =
  116.     let arr = create kind layout dims in
  117.     let dlen = Array.length dims in
  118.     match layout with
  119.     | C_layout -> cloop arr (Array.make dlen 0) f 0 dims; arr
  120.     | Fortran_layout -> floop arr (Array.make dlen 1) f (pred dlen) dims; arr
